# launchpad-studio

A tiny Node ESM release-planning toolkit that normalizes feature requests into release cards.

## Installation

```bash
npm install launchpad-studio
```

## Usage

```javascript
import { createPlanner, formatReleaseCard, validateFeature } from 'launchpad-studio';

const planner = createPlanner();
const feature = { title: 'Dark Mode', description: 'Add dark mode support' };

if (validateFeature(feature)) {
  const card = planner.normalize(feature);
  console.log(formatReleaseCard(card));
}
```

